city-focus-features-opening-day-1201770227/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影最先於2017年3月12日在[[西南偏南|西南偏南]]上作全球首映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/02/charlize-theron-atomic-blonde-the-coldest-city-title-change-sxsw-premiere-1201942727/|title=Charlize Theron MI6 Movie ‘The Coldest City’ Retitled & Will Debut At SXSW|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|date=February 22, 2017|accessdate=February 22, 2017|archive-date=2017-03-26|archive-url=https://archive.is/20170326154406/http://deadline.com/2017/02/charlize-theron-atomic-blonde-the-coldest-city-title-change-sxsw-premiere-1201942727/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 反響 ==
=== 評價 ===
《極凍之城》獲得的評價以正面居多。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於122條評論，新鮮度75%，平均得分6.6／10<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/atomic_blonde_2017 |title=Atomic Blonde (2017) |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2017-03-15 |archive-date=2017-03-26 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20170326154531/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/atomic_blonde_2017 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上則獲得62分，代表「普遍好評」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/atomic-blonde/critic-reviews |title=Atomic Blonde reviews |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2017-03-15 |archive-date=2017-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908071330/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/atomic-blonde/critic-reviews |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾在A+至F間給的評價落在「B」。

=== 票房 ===
在美國，《極凍之城》與《[[表情符號電影|表情符號電影]]》同天上映競爭，《極凍之城》預估能在首週末從三千三百間戲院中獲得2000萬美元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thewrap.com/dunkirk-atomic-blonde-emoji-movie-box-office/|title=Will ‘Dunkirk’ Stay Afloat Against ‘Atomic Blonde,’ ‘Emoji Movie’ at Box Office This Weekend?|work=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]]|date=2017-07-25|accessdate=2017-07-26|archive-date=2017-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170725235740/https://www.thewrap.com/dunkirk-atomic-blonde-emoji-movie-box-office/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國首週末票房收入達1860萬美元，位居當週票房排名第四<ref name=opening>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/07/atomic-blonde-dunkirk-emoji-movie-weekend-box-office-openings-1202138047/|title=‘Dunkirk’ Marches Ahead Of ‘Emoji Movie’ For Top Spot With $28M+|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=2017-07-30|archive-date=2017-07-30|archive-url=https://archive.is/20170730162541/http://deadline.com/2017/07/atomic-blonde-dunkirk-emoji-movie-weekend-box-office-openings-1202138047/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

